      "id": "hsm-01",
      "title": "Hosted stays still operate as Airbnb's core economic engine",
      "summary": "Public investor materials continue to anchor Airbnb around hosts, guest arrivals, booked nights, and Gross Booking Value rather than around a detached travel-superapp narrative.",
      "implication": "Prioritize guest conversion, active supply quality, and booking reliability over peripheral expansion in the base domain model.",
      "priority": "high",
